          {
        
      321. 
      
        
    321. 
          1
          
            typeset -a list
        
      322. 
      
        
    322. 
          1
          
            typeset element
        
      323.

      324.

          1

      325.

          1
          
            if (( $# ))
        
      326. 
      
        
    326. 
          1
          
            then list+=( "$@" )
        
      327. 
      
        
    327. 
          
          
            else list+=( ruby )
        
      328. 
      
        
    328. 
          
          
            fi
        
      329.

      330. 
      
        
    330. 
          3
          
            for element in "${list[@]}"
        
      331. 
      
        
    331. 
          3
          
            do requirements_$_system_name "${element}" || return $?
        
      332. 
      
        
    332. 
          
          
            done
        
      333. 
      
        
    333. 
          
          
          }
        
      334. 
      
        
    334. 
          
          
          
        
      335. 
      
        
    335. 
          
          
          #
        
      336. 
      
        
    336. 
          
          
          # rvm_autolibs_flag
        
      337. 
      
        
    337. 
          
          
          # - 0 - disabled
        
      338. 
      
        
    338. 
          
          
          # - 1 - use libs, do not install - default
        
      339. 
      
        
    339. 
          
          
          # - 2 - use libs, install if missing, fallback to 1 if brew not writable
        
      340. 
      
        
    340. 
          
          
          # - 3 - 2 + install package manager if not available
        
      341. 
      
        
    341. 
          
          
          # - 4 - 3 + error out if brew not writable, no fallback
        
      342. 
      
        
    342.

      343. 
      
        
    343. 
          
          
          __rvm_setup_compile_environment_requirements()

          1

              return 1
        
      353.

          {

          {

      378.

    380.

      390.

      391.

      392. 
      
        
    392. 
          
          
              __rvm_trust_rvmrc "$1"
        
      393.

          __rvm_parse_gems_args()

          {

          6

      635. 
      
        
    635.

      636. 
      
        
    636.

      637. 
      
        
    637.

      639. 
      
        
    639.

      640. 
      
        
    640.

      648.

      650. 
      
        
    650.

      651. 
      
        
    651.

      652. 
      
        
    652.

      653.

      654. 
      
        
    654. 
          
          
                    sed -e "s#${gem_name/ /}##" -e "s#--version[=]*[ ]*${gem_version/ /}##"
        
      655. 
      
        
    655. 
          
          
                  )" #"
        
      656. 
      
        
    656.

      657. 
      
        
    657. 
          
          
                *-v*)
        
      658. 
      
        
    658. 
          
          
                  gem_version=$(
        
      659. 
      
        
    659. 
          
          
                    echo "$gem" | sed -e 's#.*-v[=]*[ ]*##' | awk '{print $1}'
        
      660. 
      
        
    660. 
          2

      661. 
      
        
    661. 
          6

      662.

      663.

      664. 
      
        
    664. 
          2
          
                  )" #"
        
      665. 
      
        
    665. 
          2

      666. 
      
        
    666. 
          2

    667. 
          4

      668.
